    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 at all five operating points with mean bias of −4.7% and maximum deviation of 11.4%, within the 15% acceptance threshold. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under COU1 conditions.",
